+Updated stale memory-client tests to match the corrected strict validation and current public API behavior. Removed live Optimism fork dependence from package-local tests, refreshed stale block snapshots, and converted receipt-path repros to assert transaction lookup/block inclusion where the old receipt assertions depended on invalid block state roots.
